        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">Eponymous Archon</rdfs:label>
        <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">Eponymous Archon</skos:prefLabel>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">Archon that supervises family lawsuits for citizens, held by one person.</skos:definition>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="grc">ἐπώνυμος ἄρχων</rdfs:label>
        <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="grc">ἐπώνυμος ἄρχων</skos:prefLabel>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="grc">ἄρχων that supervises family lawsuits for citizens, held by one person.</skos:definition>
        <skos:example xml:lang="grc">Dem. 21.9: "ἐν δὲ ταύτῃ ἐπειδὰν χρηματίσωσιν οἱ πρόεδροι περὶ ὧν διῴκηκεν ὁ ἄρχων, χρηματίζειν καὶ περὶ ὧν ἄν τις ἠδικηκὼς ᾖ περὶ τὴν ἑορτὴν ἢ παρανενομηκώς"</skos:example>
